# Sound Effects

Short sound effect files for game events.

## Recommended Files

### Player Sounds
- player_shot.wav - Player firing sound
- player_special.wav - Special weapon sound
- player_hit.wav - Player taking damage

### Enemy Sounds
- enemy_shot.wav - Enemy firing sound
- enemy_explode.wav - Enemy destruction
- boss_warning.wav - Boss warning siren

### UI Sounds
- menu_select.wav - Menu selection
- menu_confirm.wav - Confirm action
- menu_back.wav - Back/cancel action

### Gameplay Sounds
- powerup_collect.wav - Collecting power-ups
- explosion_small.wav - Small explosion
- explosion_large.wav - Large explosion

Use .ogg or .wav format. Ask @audio to integrate sounds!
